ED_Title: High-level plenary meeting to commemorate the one-hundredth anniversary of the establishment of the International Labour Organization
ED_DecisionText: At its 74th plenary meeting, on 10 April 2019, the General Assembly decided, without setting a precedent, to invite the President of the Economic and Social Council to make a statement at the high-level plenary meeting to commemorate the one-hundredth anniversary of the establishment of the International Labour Organization.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of this decision will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/73/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
